QuestData.Title: Rusty Tube
QuestData.Description:
<The malfunctioning junkbot is now a mere heap of metal, its signature tube poking out of the remains.
You remove the tube. The citizens of Rustbolt seem to trade in junk, maybe someone will want it.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Show the Rusty Tube to Vera Lonelycog in Rustbolt on Mechagon Island.
